"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mho1665703160155.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mho1665703160155.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mho1665703160155.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mho1665703160155\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This method returns the types of the occurrence’s fields.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mho1665703160155__topic_d129569e1_d129570e1_d129571e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mho1665703160155__p_d129572e1_d129573e1_d129574e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">import\n               com.rocketsoftware.uniface.jci.*;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mho1665703160155__p_d129575e1_d129576e1_d129577e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">int[] getFieldTypes()</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mho1665703160155__section_vmc_bzc_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d207845e64\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mho1665703160155__p_d129581e1_d129582e1_d129583e1\">Return the types of the occurrence’s fields.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mho1665703160155__section_vtl_czc_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d207845e73\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mho1665703160155__p_d129554e1_d129555e1_d129556e1\">The constants used for Uniface field types are\n            listed in the following table:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mho1665703160155__table_d15389e1_d15390e1_d15391e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Field Type Constants</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mho1665703160155__table_d15389e1_d1